data.title: CIPC Publication Template - AR DEREGISTRATION Version K 2.1
data.meta_description: CIPC Publication Template - AR DEREGISTRATION Version K 2.1 - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. This document provides a notice from the Companies and Intellectual Property Commission (CIPC) of South Africa announcing the final deregistration of several companies and close corporations due to failure to submit annual returns. It lists over 200 company names that will be deregistered according to Section 82 of the Companies Act of 2008. The notice serves to inform the general public of these deregistrations.
